### GHL API - Testes diretos (REST Client extension)
### Substituir {{GHL_API_KEY}} pela chave real

@baseUrl = https://services.leadconnectorhq.com
@apiKey = {{GHL_API_KEY}}
@locationId = ehlHgDeJS3sr8rCDcZtA
@version = 2021-07-28

### 1. Get Location (testar auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations/{{locationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Version: {{version}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Pipelines
GET {{baseUrl}}/opportunities/pipelines?locationId={{locationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Version: {{version}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Search Opportunities (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/opportunities/search?location_id={{locationId}}&status=all&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Version: {{version}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get Calendar Events (ultimos 30 dias)
GET {{baseUrl}}/calendars/events?locationId={{locationId}}&startTime=1736726400000&endTime=1739404800000
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Version: {{version}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get Contacts (page 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contacts/?locationId={{locationId}}&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}
Version: {{version}}
Accept: application/json
